comments.value: #Sorted Alogrithm for SPL003 :: Sorting requirement. Rule #1 Movies with genre_ids == null should be first in response. Rule #2, if multiple movies have genre_ids == null, then sort by id (ascending). For movies that have non-null genre_ids, results should be sorted by id (ascending)
